The dub. This is one of the first GOOD dubs made by the Americans. I think even the dub haters should at least respect the work. That said, the Original audio has great feels and tones as well. \
However, the stage of the show is in this multi cultural space. All sorts of people from different nationalities tag alone. I don't know about the Japanese version but the English does have great accent and it just feels right that a cowboy speaks English, isn't it? \
